{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_09_01_short",
  "title": "天動瑠依 1話 か、か、間接 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夏祭り当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Summer Festival Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "会場、まだ夕方なのに凄く賑わってます\nお祭りって、こんなに沢山人が来るんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The venue is already bustling even though it's only evening.\nSo many people come to festivals‚ don't they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日のお祭りは、日本有数の規模だからな\nこの後ステージが控えてるけど、緊張してないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because today's festival is one of the largest in Japan.\nYou have a stage performance coming up. Are you nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 19.233333226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "今回は、私一人でのステージですからね\nお気遣いありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time it's a stage performance by myself.\nThank you for your concern.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 25.2666665594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、大丈夫です。ソロで舞台に立つ機会は\n少ないですけど、ワクワクしてるくらいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I'm fine. I don't get many opportunities\nto stand on stage solo‚ but I'm excited about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それは心強いな。瑠依のパフォーマンスで盛り上げて\n地方の人達にもアピールしていこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's reassuring. Let's liven things up with your performance\nand appeal to the local people too‚ Rui.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 38.9999998927
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 41.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、頑張ります\n……ところで、まだ本番まで時間がありますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'll do my best.\n…By the way‚ we still have time until the show‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくなので、少しだけお祭りを\n見て回りたいんですけど……いいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we have this opportunity‚ I'd like to look around\nthe festival for a bit… would that be okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 51.9666665594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "時間はあるし、構わないけど\n分かった、それなら俺も一緒に行くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have time‚ so it's fine.\nOkay‚ then I'll go with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}